    "en": {
      "title": "The money found in the presidential palace will be handed over to the court",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The amount of rupees one crore and seventy-eight lakhs that the activists handed over to the police while at the President's House was handed over to the Colombo Fort Magistrate's Court today (29) by the Divisional Criminal Investigation Units.",
        "The money was handed over by the Divisional Crime Investigation Unit before Colombo Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage.",
        "The Magistrate also ordered the Director of the Special Crime Investigation Unit to immediately submit a report to the court regarding the delay of more than three weeks in providing this amount to the court.",
        "After President's Attorney Mr. Rienzi Arsakularatne informed the court on the 28th yesterday why the Fort Police did not hand over the money to the court even though it had been more than three weeks since the money was given to them, a court order was issued to hand over the money to the court immediately.",
        "Accordingly, today 29, the amount was handed over to the court not by the Fort Police but by the Divisional Criminal Investigation Unit."
      ],
